<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration - Kiddies Quizzes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Bubblegum+Sans|Flavors">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Registration</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Kiddies Quizzes! To help protect your account and keep your points safe, please select two digital guardians below. Your guardians will watch over your account and ensure that no one else can access it without your permission.</p>
        <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

            <p>Select Your Digital Guardians:</p>
            <div class="guardians">
                <!-- Guardians will be dynamically added here -->
            </div>
            <input type="hidden" id="guardians" name="guardians" value="">
            
            <button id="nextBtn" type="submit">Next</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
